{"tid":326901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★廢老轉行做三行，梯間跌倒失救亡 !","createTime":"2017-07-18T10:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T05:07:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96f69293be63e05136a2a5a33d55f3d170ab1a77","tid":326901,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">助舊友做臨時幫工　裝修男疑梯間跌倒失救亡</span><br />\n<br />\n觀塘康寧道一住宅大廈梯間發現男屍，疑跌倒失救致死。早上8時許，觀塘康寧道一幢住宅大廈， 姓黃街坊（33歲）發現一名男子倒臥在8至9樓梯間，於是報警。救護員到場，證實該名男子已告身亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查後，證實死者姓張（61歲），其後聯絡上死者妻子到場認屍，初步相信事件無可疑，惟死因有待驗屍確定。期間張妻傷心激動，嚎哭：「點解你哋唔報警，點解唔送佢去醫院」。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者曾做裝修，年紀漸老及經家人勸喻下改任保安，於尖沙咀一大廈工作。他近日受舊工友邀請，往上址9樓一單位做臨時工幫忙清拆，初步不排除期間他在梯間跌倒昏迷，致失救死亡。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170718/bkn-20170718104629727-0718_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170718%2Fbkn-20170718104629727-0718_00822_001.html&d=DNbAz9IKmuUlXoNkJJ8oYgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7294c77a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170718/bkn-20170718104629727-0718_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"47d23b8ac725bc2650af8d4bab3e8c72b293e2b5","tid":326901,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeeaea36e92adc60518ccbe33a5aee7b69d2af44","tid":326901,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"不自量力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f812b